drug.toxicity:
LD50, oral, rat = 18100 mg/kg; 
LD50, oral, mouse = 14500 mg/kg;
LD50, IV, rat = 3600 - 7300 mg/kg;
LD50, IV, mouse = 5400 - 10900 mg/kg;
LD50, IV, dog = >2200 mg/kg

drug.clearance:
Clearance may be lower in older patients. 
Total serum clearance (CLtot) = 250 mL/min;
Renal clearance (CLr) = 120 mL/min
